<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2292] Binding is not passed to the script if the parsed script text contains no statements</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2292</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This looks like a very exotic use case. But if you do a lot of automatic script generation, this is a real nuisance. You have to always put some dummy statement into the text to make things work.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
